values:
Back!    Thought I'd post a quick...erm...post about what's been going on with me.

I'm back off to Japan in 2 weeks....not to study this time, though.  I'll be working!  I'm excited that I don't have to jump between countries anymore just because of school.

Again, I usually use Myspace, so hit me up on there if you can.

I'll try to start posting here more often!  I just gotta pretty it up a bit....

I'm back in the United States bitches.
For how long, no one knows...haha
If you want to check out my shit, go to www.myspace.com/joshjp

Hey, I don't really LJ anymore...not that I ever did, either...heh.  Anyway, I post at my website and Xanga now.  If you don't know those, then you probably don't DESERVE to know them....haha.  Anyway, I'm out for now.  Just using this so I can post in my friend's LJ's.

Lates.

I haven't written in here in awhile.  I'll type up something quick.  Well, I've been playing FFVII a little bit today and I really forgot how much I enjoyed that game.  I really can't wait for FFXII.  Good times.

What else?  Nothing much.  Check out www.joshinthe.net for real updated and pictures from Japan.  I'm gettin ready to go downstairs and maybe get some food.  I've been in my room on the game for the past couple of hours.  

later.

Hey, just updating to tell you to check out m_lapis_lazuli's page!

And check out my real journal at http://joshinthe.net

anyway, I'm done here.  Later

Just testing this out b/c i'm making it for a friend.  easier than xanga?

Josh
